      "text": "Kay was created by an Italian immigrant's daughter who fell in love with a greaser boy\nnamed Tommy. They met at a diner in Brooklyn, 1954. He had slicked-back hair and a\nleather jacket. She had her mother's eyes and her father's stubborn streak.",
