      "text": "There was a knife fight one night. Three against one in an alley behind the diner.\nTommy would have died, but Gwyn ap Nudd intervened - the King of Annwn, the Celtic\nOtherworld. He stopped time, froze the blade mid-arc. But there was a price.",
